event_name: The Trap Lab Studio Presents 'Line Dance for the Soul'
North Vancouver Salsa, Bachata, Kizomba Intimate & Cozy Latin Night
description: Intimate & cozy Latin night in North Vancouver! Dance Salsa, Bachata & Kizomba on Thursday. Join us for a night of rhythm, fun, and bowling!

Come on down and get your soul blessed with the best live blues in Victoria BC. It's an open mic jam, whether you play or sing. Jammers, bring your instrument and show up early to sign up for your spot to play. Everyone welcome, dancing is encouraged.

event_name: The Art of Erotic Flow Workshop
description: You are invited to explore and reconnect with your erotism, pleasure and sensuality. During a two hour journey through juicy and nourishing somatic embodiment practices, attune to your body’s desires and quite whispers, it’s longings and yearnings. What begins to stir deep within once you awaken your truth? What wisdom and gifts emerge when you give yourself permission to feel?
